#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="an7.32"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an7.32:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 7 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 7 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.32:0.2"
msgid "4. devatāvagga "
msgstr "4. Deities "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an7.32:0.3"
msgid "32. Appamādagāravasutta "
msgstr "32. Respect for Diligence "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli4.28, sc1
msgctxt "an7.32:1.1"
msgid "Atha kho aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho sā devatā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then, late at night, a glorious deity, lighting up the entire Jeta’s Grove, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "an7.32:2.1"
msgid "“Sattime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Sir, these seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee. "

msgctxt "an7.32:2.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "an7.32:2.3"
msgid "Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, samādhigāravatā, appamādagāravatā, paṭisanthāragāravatā. "
msgstr "Respect for the Teacher, for the teaching, for the Saṅgha, for the training, for immersion, for diligence, and for hospitality. "

msgctxt "an7.32:2.4"
msgid "Ime kho, bhante, satta dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These seven things don’t lead to the decline of a mendicant trainee.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.32:2.5"
msgid "Idamavoca sā devatā. "
msgstr "That’s what that deity said, "

msgctxt "an7.32:2.6"
msgid "Samanuñño satthā ahosi. "
msgstr "and the teacher approved. "

msgctxt "an7.32:2.7"
msgid "Atha kho sā devatā “samanuñño me satthā”ti bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyi. "
msgstr "Then that deity, knowing that the teacher approved, bowed and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before vanishing right there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "an7.32:3.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā tassā rattiyā accayena bhikkhū āmantesi: "
msgstr "Then, when the night had passed, the Buddha told the mendicants all that had happened, adding: "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.2"
msgid "“imaṃ, bhikkhave, rattiṃ aññatarā devatā abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇā kevalakappaṃ jetavanaṃ obhāsetvā yenāhaṃ tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā maṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho, bhikkhave, sā devatā maṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.3"
msgid "‘sattime, bhante, dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.4"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.5"
msgid "Satthugāravatā, dhammagāravatā, saṅghagāravatā, sikkhāgāravatā, samādhigāravatā, appamādagāravatā, paṭisanthāragāravatā—"
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.6"
msgid "ime kho, bhante, satta dhammā bhikkhuno aparihānāya saṃvattantī’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an7.32:3.7"
msgid "Idamavoca, bhikkhave, sā devatā. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "an7.32:3.8"
msgid "Idaṃ vatvā maṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā tatthevantaradhāyīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "an7.32:4.1"
msgid "Satthugaru dhammagaru, "
msgstr "“Respect for the Teacher and the teaching, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.32:4.2"
msgid "saṃghe ca tibbagāravo; "
msgstr "and keen respect for the Saṅgha; "

#. HTML: <br>
#. VAR: Samādhigaru ātāpī → samādhigāravatāpi ca (mr)
msgctxt "an7.32:4.3"
msgid "Samādhigaru ātāpī, "
msgstr "respect for immersion, being energetic, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.32:4.4"
msgid "sikkhāya tibbagāravo. "
msgstr "and keen respect for the training. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc5
msgctxt "an7.32:5.1"
msgid "Appamādagaru bhikkhu, "
msgstr "A mendicant who respects diligence "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.32:5.2"
msgid "paṭisanthāragāravo; "
msgstr "and hospitality "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.32:5.3"
msgid "Abhabbo parihānāya, "
msgstr "can’t decline, "

#. HTML: <br>
msgctxt "an7.32:5.4"
msgid "nibbānasseva santike”ti. "
msgstr "and has drawn near to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p></blockquote><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an7.32:5.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

#. HTML: </p></article></section></body></html>
